# Global configuration section
#   Values here are used as defaults for any following Channel section that
#   doesn't specify them.
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
# By default (CopyArrivalDate no), if you copy an old email from inbox to
# Archive (e.g.) it will get the date of the copy assigned, instead of just
# keeping its original date of arrival! Also see:
# https://rakhim.org/fastmail-setup-with-emacs-mu4e-and-mbsync-on-macos/
# https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Isync#Emails_on_remote_server_have_the_wrong_date
CopyArrivalDate yes

## --- IMAPAccount (Mail.ru) ---

IMAPAccount d3v1ant@mail.ru
Host imap.mail.ru
User d3v1ant@mail.ru
PassCmd "pass email/mail.ru/d3v1ant-mu4e"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
Timeout 120

MaildirStore d3v1ant@mail.ru-local
Path ~/.mail/mailru/d3v1ant/
Inbox ~/.mail/mailru/d3v1ant/Inbox
# SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore d3v1ant@mail.ru-remote
Account d3v1ant@mail.ru

Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-inbox
Far :d3v1ant@mail.ru-remote:"INBOX"
Near :d3v1ant@mail.ru-local:"INBOX"

Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-trash
Far :d3v1ant@mail.ru-remote:"Корзина"
Near :d3v1ant@mail.ru-local:"Trash"

Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-spam
Far :d3v1ant@mail.ru-remote:"Спам"
Near :d3v1ant@mail.ru-local:"Spam"

Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-drafts
Far :d3v1ant@mail.ru-remote:"Черновики"
Near :d3v1ant@mail.ru-local:"Drafts"

Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-sent
Far :d3v1ant@mail.ru-remote:"Отправленные"
Near :d3v1ant@mail.ru-local:"Sent"

Group d3v1ant@mail.ru
Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-inbox
Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-trash
Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-spam
Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-drafts
Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-archive
Channel d3v1ant@mail.ru-sent

